        <p class="doc-p">After purchase, you will be asked to complete an intake (by audio recording or written form). Your Resonance.ID is cultivated by hand based on your intake and delivered to you, by email, as a private link.</p>
        <p class="doc-p">We aim to deliver your Resonance.ID <strong>within 7 days</strong> of receiving your completed intake. This is a target, not a guarantee; if a delay arises we will let you know.</p>
        <p class="doc-p">Resonance.ID <strong>does not include revisions</strong>. The deliverable is provided once, in final form. A short walk-through conversation may be offered after delivery; this is for clarification and orientation, not for revising or re-doing the deliverable.</p>
      </div>

