        <p class="doc-p">Resonance.SITE is a service engagement governed by a separate written agreement that defines scope, milestones, timeline, revisions, and total fee. These Terms apply alongside that agreement. Where the two conflict, the separate written agreement prevails.</p>
        <p class="doc-p">A non-refundable deposit is payable before work begins. The remaining balance and its payment schedule are set out in your agreement.</p>
